products.description: A quintessential Napa Valley Cabernet, this wine offers an inviting profile that balances fruit intensity with structure. It opens with aromas of dark plum, blackberry, and a hint of mocha. The palate is smooth and well-rounded, featuring flavors of ripe black cherry and vanilla spice, supported by supple tannins that lead to a satisfying finish.

products.fullName: Force & Grace Cabernet Sauvignon Paso 750 Ml
products.description: This Paso Robles Cabernet Sauvignon is a testament to the region's ability to produce bold, expressive wines. Force & Grace delivers a powerful aromatic profile of black cherry, ripe currant, and a touch of savory dried herbs. The palate is full-bodied and rich, with a firm tannic structure that supports its deep, dark fruit flavors.

Sourced from vineyards across the renowned Napa Valley, this Cabernet Sauvignon is crafted with a focus on elegance and balance. It presents an alluring bouquet of boysenberry, black cherry, and a hint of cedar. The palate is rich and layered, with a velvety texture and well-integrated tannins that carry through to a long, polished finish.

From their estate vineyards in Napa Valley, this Allomi Cabernet Sauvignon is a bold and structured wine. It showcases the warmer climate of the region with its deep aromas of black cherry, plum, and espresso. The palate is full-bodied with well-integrated tannins, delivering concentrated dark fruit flavors complemented by a touch of oak spice.

products.fullName: The Calling Paso Robles Cabernet Sauvignon
products.description: A definitive statement from the sun-drenched terroir of Paso Robles, this Cabernet Sauvignon is both powerful and polished. It opens with an inviting bouquet of dark cherry, ripe plum, and a hint of graphite. The palate is a well-structured tapestry of black currant and cocoa, supported by firm tannins that lead to a satisfyingly long finish.

With a long history in Napa Valley, Beaulieu Vineyard (BV) consistently delivers classic Cabernet Sauvignon. This wine, sourced from their Rutherford and Calistoga vineyards, offers inviting aromas of black cherry, raspberry, and a touch of oak. The palate is smooth and approachable, with soft tannins and a balanced finish for enjoyment.

Crafted by winemaker Joe Wagner, this Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon is a rich and complex tapestry of flavors. It is a bold, fruit-forward wine that entices with aromas of dark chocolate, blackberry jam, and a hint of vanilla. The palate is lush and velvety, with a fine tannic structure that provides balance to its opulent, dark fruit character.

products.fullName: Louis M Martini Napa Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: A benchmark for Napa Valley Cabernet, this wine from Louis M. Martini is both classic and compelling. It opens with a rich bouquet of black cherry, blackberry, and savory herbs. The palate is full-bodied and well-structured, with concentrated dark fruit flavors, firm tannins, and a touch of cedar spice that leads to a long, elegant finish.

From the legendary Wagner family, this California-appellated Cabernet Sauvignon is made in the signature Caymus style. It is rich, opulent, and fruit-driven, with lush aromas of blackberry, cassis, and cocoa. The palate is velvety and smooth, with a ripe, textural character and a distinctive hint of vanilla on its long, supple finish.

From the historic Stags' Leap Winery, this Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon is a model of grace and power. It reveals intricate layers of blackberry, cassis, and black cherry, interwoven with notes of mocha and spice. Known for its "iron fist in a velvet glove" quality, its robust tannins and balanced acidity promise exceptional aging potential.
products.location: Stags Leap District, Napa Valley, California

products.fullName: Orin Swift Palermo Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: A bold and artistic blend from winemaker Dave Phinney, Palermo is a quintessential Napa Valley Cabernet. It is an opulent and powerful wine, with an intense aromatic profile of black cherry, cassis, and roasted espresso. The palate is massive and concentrated, with a rich texture, firm tannins, and a finish that is both long and luxurious.

Perched atop DAOU Mountain in Paso Robles, this Reserve Cabernet is a masterful expression of its terroir. This luxurious wine is profoundly concentrated, offering an aromatic explosion of black fruit, licorice, and espresso. The palate is rich and velvety, delivering waves of ripe blackberry and dark chocolate on a long and elegant finish.

Known for their rich and expressive style, Rombauer's Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon is a luxurious and decadent wine. It entices with aromas of black currant, ripe plum, and a hint of vanilla. The palate is full-bodied and velvety, with soft, supple tannins and a core of sweet, dark fruit that leads to a long, smooth, and satisfying finish.

products.fullName: Stags Leap Wine Cellars Est Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: From the winery that won the historic 1976 Judgement of Paris, the Artemis Cabernet Sauvignon is a Napa Valley icon. It offers alluring aromas of black cherry, raspberry, and a hint of vanilla. The palate is medium-bodied and elegant, with a seamless texture, fine-grained tannins, and a beautiful balance of fruit, spice, and savory notes.
products.location: Stags Leap District, Napa Valley, California

products.description: Sourced from venerable vineyards in Napa Valley, this Chardonnay from Stags' Leap Winery balances richness with vibrant acidity. Aromas of crisp apple, pear, and a hint of lemon zest mingle with delicate notes of toasted almond. The wine’s time in oak lends a subtle creaminess that is beautifully offset by a refreshing minerality.

products.fullName: Stags Leap Wine Cellars Chardonnay 750 Ml
products.description: The Karia Chardonnay from Stags' Leap Wine Cellars is a vibrant and refreshing expression of Napa Valley. It is fermented in a mix of stainless steel and neutral oak to preserve its bright aromatics. It offers notes of crisp pear, lemon curd, and a touch of white flower, with a lively acidity and a clean, elegant, mineral-driven finish.

Representing the celebrated Russian River Valley, this Pinot Noir is both bold and sophisticated. It presents a captivating nose of ripe strawberry, black cherry, and a touch of earthy forest floor. The palate is plush and smooth, with flavors of raspberry, plum, and a whisper of clove spice, all framed by well-integrated tannins.

Sourced from a cool-climate vineyard in the Russian River Valley, this Pinot Noir is an elegant and nuanced wine. It opens with delicate aromas of red cherry, raspberry, and a hint of rose petal. The palate is refined and silky, with a bright acidity that highlights its pure red fruit character, leading to a long and graceful finish.

products.fullName: Belle Glos Dairyman Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: From a windswept vineyard in the Russian River Valley, the Dairyman Pinot Noir is a powerful and expressive wine. It showcases deep, concentrated aromas of wild blackberry, dark cherry, and a hint of cedar. The palate is opulently textured, delivering lush flavors of ripe plum and cocoa powder framed by velvety tannins that lead to a dramatic finish.

products.fullName: Belle Glos Las Alturas Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: Hailing from the Santa Lucia Highlands, Las Alturas is one of the boldest expressions in the Belle Glos lineup. It is a dark and intensely concentrated Pinot Noir, with powerful aromas of blackberry, dark chocolate, and a hint of vanilla. The palate is rich and full-bodied, with a velvety texture and a long, powerful finish.

products.fullName: Belle Glos Clark And Telephone Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: Sourced from a renowned vineyard in the Santa Maria Valley, this Pinot Noir is striking in its depth and complexity. It bursts from the glass with effusive aromas of black cherry, raspberry, and crushed violets. The palate is rich and expansive, with supple tannins and a distinctive note of wild berry jam on the long, smooth finish.

This Sonoma County Pinot Noir is a beautifully balanced and versatile wine from J Vineyards. It offers an appealing bouquet of black cherry, raspberry, and a hint of forest floor. The palate is silky and medium-bodied, with a bright acidity that provides a lovely counterpoint to its ripe fruit flavors, making it elegant and food-friendly.

A shining example of Californian sparkling wine, the J Cuvée 20 Brut is both lively and elegant. It features delicate notes of toasted almond, crisp green apple, and a hint of wild strawberry. The fine, persistent bubbles create a wonderfully creamy texture on the palate, leading to a refreshing and vibrant finish that is perfect for any occasion.

A classic from the heart of Champagne, this Brut is renowned for its structure and vivacity. A majority of Pinot Noir in the blend provides a wonderful framework for its bright aromas of fresh pear, citrus, and a touch of brioche. The palate is crisp and full-bodied, with a harmonious balance of fruit and acidity that culminates in a clean, zesty finish.

As the successor to the historic "White Star," Moët Impérial carries on a legacy of celebration from Champagne. This iconic brut is distinguished by its bright fruitiness and elegant maturity. It reveals a delightful bouquet of green apple, citrus, and white flowers, with notes of brioche and fresh nuts. The palate is seductive, lively, and generous.

An icon of Champagne, Veuve Clicquot's Yellow Label is renowned for its consistency and quality. Dominated by Pinot Noir, it offers a perfect balance of power and finesse. Aromas of yellow apple, pear, and brioche lead to a full-bodied palate with a creamy texture and a long, satisfying finish with a distinctive toasty character.

products.fullName: Columbia Crest Est Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: This Cabernet Sauvignon is a benchmark for the exceptional value and quality found in Washington's Columbia Valley. It offers a classic and approachable profile, with inviting aromas of dark cherry, blackberry, and a hint of vanilla. The palate is smooth and well-balanced, featuring ripe fruit flavors, soft tannins, and a touch of oak spice.
products.Description: Perched atop DAOU Mountain in Paso Robles, this Reserve Cabernet is a masterful expression of its terroir. This luxurious wine is profoundly concentrated, offering an aromatic explosion of black fruit, licorice, and espresso. The palate is rich and velvety, delivering waves of ripe blackberry and dark chocolate on a long and elegant finish.

products.description: Grown in the high-elevation vineyards of Lake County, California, this sustainably farmed Cabernet Sauvignon is both rugged and refined. The wine opens with bold aromas of black cherry, currant, and a touch of savory herbs. On the palate, it is full-bodied and well-structured, with flavors of dark fruit, espresso, and spice, supported by firm tannins.
products.Description: Known for their rich and expressive style, Rombauer's Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon is a luxurious and decadent wine. It entices with aromas of black currant, ripe plum, and a hint of vanilla. The palate is full-bodied and velvety, with soft, supple tannins and a core of sweet, dark fruit that leads to a long, smooth, and satisfying finish.

products.fullName: Sterling Vintners Collection Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: A quintessential California Cabernet, this wine from Sterling's Vintners Collection is crafted for immediate enjoyment. It brings together fruit from across the state to create a profile that is rich and fruit-forward. Aromas of blackberry, dark cherry, and mocha lead to a smooth, medium-bodied palate with soft tannins and a pleasing touch of spice.
products.Product Name.1: STAGS LEAP WINE CELLARS EST CABERNET SAUVIGNON 750 ML
products.Description: From the winery that won the historic 1976 Judgement of Paris, the Artemis Cabernet Sauvignon is a Napa Valley icon. It offers alluring aromas of black cherry, raspberry, and a hint of vanilla. The palate is medium-bodied and elegant, with a seamless texture, fine-grained tannins, and a beautiful balance of fruit, spice, and savory notes.
products.Location/Region: Stags Leap District, Napa Valley, California

products.fullName: Bread And Butter Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: True to its name, this California Cabernet Sauvignon is designed to be a comforting and reliable favorite. It presents a straightforward and appealing character, with lush aromas of blackberry jam, vanilla, and toasted oak. The palate is smooth and mellow, with ripe, dark fruit flavors, a hint of mocha, and a soft, easy-drinking finish.
products.Description: Sourced from venerable vineyards in Napa Valley, this Chardonnay from Stags' Leap Winery balances richness with vibrant acidity. Aromas of crisp apple, pear, and a hint of lemon zest mingle with delicate notes of toasted almond. The wine’s time in oak lends a subtle creaminess that is beautifully offset by a refreshing minerality.

products.description: This single-vineyard Cabernet Sauvignon from Louis M. Martini is a tribute to a historic Napa Valley site. It is a powerful and age-worthy wine, displaying intense aromas of blackcurrant, dark chocolate, and anise. The palate is concentrated and deeply layered with flavors of ripe blackberry and espresso, all framed by muscular tannins.
products.Product Name.1: STAGS LEAP WINE CELLARS CHARDONNAY 750 ML
products.Description: The Karia Chardonnay from Stags' Leap Wine Cellars is a vibrant and refreshing expression of Napa Valley. It is fermented in a mix of stainless steel and neutral oak to preserve its bright aromatics. It offers notes of crisp pear, lemon curd, and a touch of white flower, with a lively acidity and a clean, elegant, mineral-driven finish.

products.description: A bold expression from California's Central Coast, this Cabernet Sauvignon is known for its robust and fruit-driven style. The wine captures the region's warm climate with its powerful aromas of ripe plum, black cherry, and a hint of black pepper. The palate is full-bodied and rich, with luscious dark fruit flavors and well-integrated tannins.
products.Description: Representing the celebrated Russian River Valley, this Pinot Noir is both bold and sophisticated. It presents a captivating nose of ripe strawberry, black cherry, and a touch of earthy forest floor. The palate is plush and smooth, with flavors of raspberry, plum, and a whisper of clove spice, all framed by well-integrated tannins.

products.description: Grown on the rugged hillsides of California, this Cabernet Sauvignon is as powerful as its name suggests. The challenging terrain forces the vines to produce grapes with intense concentration and character. The resulting wine is bold and unapologetic, with massive flavors of black currant, licorice, and vanilla, all supported by a firm structure.
products.Description: Sourced from a cool-climate vineyard in the Russian River Valley, this Pinot Noir is an elegant and nuanced wine. It opens with delicate aromas of red cherry, raspberry, and a hint of rose petal. The palate is refined and silky, with a bright acidity that highlights its pure red fruit character, leading to a long and graceful finish.

products.fullName: Charles Woodson Intercept Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: From NFL star Charles Woodson, this Paso Robles Cabernet Sauvignon is crafted with passion and precision. It's a full-bodied wine that is both approachable and complex, offering aromas of dark chocolate, black cherry, and baking spices. The palate is rich and smooth, with flavors of ripe blackberry, vanilla, and a hint of toast from the oak barrels.
products.Product Name.1: BELLE GLOS DAIRYMAN PINOT NOIR 750 ML
products.Description: From a windswept vineyard in the Russian River Valley, the Dairyman Pinot Noir is a powerful and expressive wine. It showcases deep, concentrated aromas of wild blackberry, dark cherry, and a hint of cedar. The palate is opulently textured, delivering lush flavors of ripe plum and cocoa powder framed by velvety tannins that lead to a dramatic finish.

products.description: Created by the Wagner family of Caymus fame, Bonanza is a multi-vintage California Cabernet that delivers consistent quality and value. It is crafted from a "bonanza" of vineyards across the state, resulting in a wine that is smooth, rich, and easy to love. It features notes of dark fruit, plums, and a hint of leather with a soft, supple texture.
products.Product Name.1: BELLE GLOS LAS ALTURAS PINOT NOIR 750 ML
products.Description: Hailing from the Santa Lucia Highlands, Las Alturas is one of the boldest expressions in the Belle Glos lineup. It is a dark and intensely concentrated Pinot Noir, with powerful aromas of blackberry, dark chocolate, and a hint of vanilla. The palate is rich and full-bodied, with a velvety texture and a long, powerful finish.

products.description: This "Limited" release from Decoy is a step up in complexity, showcasing the art of blending from Sonoma County's finest vineyards. It reveals alluring aromas of boysenberry, black cherry, and milk chocolate, with underlying hints of cedar and spice. The palate is rich and concentrated, with a beautiful texture and plush, well-integrated tannins.
products.Product Name.1: BELLE GLOS CLARK AND TELEPHONE PINOT NOIR 750 ML
products.Description: Sourced from a renowned vineyard in the Santa Maria Valley, this Pinot Noir is striking in its depth and complexity. It bursts from the glass with effusive aromas of black cherry, raspberry, and crushed violets. The palate is rich and expansive, with supple tannins and a distinctive note of wild berry jam on the long, smooth finish.

products.description: This flagship Cabernet Sauvignon from DAOU is a quintessential expression of Paso Robles' mountainous terroir. It is a rich and compelling wine, with a captivating nose of black cherry, licorice, and Zante currant. The palate is full-bodied and exquisitely balanced, featuring flavors of blackberry and dark chocolate supported by silky tannins.
products.Description: This Sonoma County Pinot Noir is a beautifully balanced and versatile wine from J Vineyards. It offers an appealing bouquet of black cherry, raspberry, and a hint of forest floor. The palate is silky and medium-bodied, with a bright acidity that provides a lovely counterpoint to its ripe fruit flavors, making it elegant and food-friendly.

products.description: Sourced from the estate Maverick Ranch vineyard in Napa Valley, this Cabernet Sauvignon is a testament to sustainable farming and meticulous winemaking. It offers a complex bouquet of red currant, blackberry, and cedar. On the palate, the wine is well-structured, with layered flavors of dark fruit, mocha, and a touch of vanilla that lead to a polished finish.
products.Description: A shining example of Californian sparkling wine, the J Cuvée 20 Brut is both lively and elegant. It features delicate notes of toasted almond, crisp green apple, and a hint of wild strawberry. The fine, persistent bubbles create a wonderfully creamy texture on the palate, leading to a refreshing and vibrant finish that is perfect for any occasion.

products.description: A classic from Washington's Columbia Valley, this Chardonnay is crafted in a fresh, soft style with bright apple and sweet citrus fruit character. It has an appealing texture and balanced acidity that is complemented by a subtle touch of spice and vanilla from light oak aging. It is a versatile and refreshing wine, perfect for pairing with a wide variety of foods.
products.Description: A classic from the heart of Champagne, this Brut is renowned for its structure and vivacity. A majority of Pinot Noir in the blend provides a wonderful framework for its bright aromas of fresh pear, citrus, and a touch of brioche. The palate is crisp and full-bodied, with a harmonious balance of fruit and acidity that culminates in a clean, zesty finish.

products.description: This Chardonnay from Sterling's Vintners Collection is a beautifully expressive California white wine. It is crafted to be bright and approachable, with alluring aromas of ripe pineapple, green apple, and lemon zest. The palate is lively and refreshing, with a smooth texture and just a hint of vanilla and toasted oak, making it a well-balanced wine.
products.Description: As the successor to the historic "White Star," Moët Impérial carries on a legacy of celebration from Champagne. This iconic brut is distinguished by its bright fruitiness and elegant maturity. It reveals a delightful bouquet of green apple, citrus, and white flowers, with notes of brioche and fresh nuts. The palate is seductive, lively, and generous.

products.description: A pioneer in organic farming, Bonterra crafts this Chardonnay from 100% organically grown grapes in Mendocino County. The wine opens with vibrant aromas of green apple, pear, and citrus. The palate is crisp and clean, with a touch of creaminess from partial malolactic fermentation that adds notes of butter. It's a balanced wine that is refreshing.
products.Description: An icon of Champagne, Veuve Clicquot's Yellow Label is renowned for its consistency and quality. Dominated by Pinot Noir, it offers a perfect balance of power and finesse. Aromas of yellow apple, pear, and brioche lead to a full-bodied palate with a creamy texture and a long, satisfying finish with a distinctive toasty character.

products.description: An unoaked Chardonnay from the Santa Lucia Highlands, Mer Soleil Silver is fermented and aged in concrete tanks to preserve its fresh, vibrant character. This unique process yields a wine with striking aromas of lemon blossom, white peach, and a distinctive wet stone minerality. The palate is crisp and lively, with a roundness of texture and a clean finish.

This Columbia Valley Chardonnay is a beautifully consistent and approachable wine from one of Washington's most celebrated producers. It opens with bright aromas of crisp apple and sweet citrus. The palate is soft and inviting, with a refreshing acidity that is nicely balanced by a subtle layer of spice and vanilla from its gentle oak aging.

Sourced from the heart of the Russian River Valley, Raeburn Chardonnay is a stunningly balanced and aromatic white wine. It begins with beautiful aromas of white pear, baked apple, and a touch of toasted oak. The palate is lush and creamy yet remains vibrant, with flavors of citrus zest and vanilla that culminate in a long, elegant finish.

products.fullName: J Vineyards Multi Appelation Chardonnay 750 Ml
products.description: This Chardonnay from J Vineyards is a thoughtful blend of grapes from premier California appellations. It offers an appealing bouquet of ripe pear, golden apple, and a hint of tropical fruit. The palate is rich yet balanced, with a creamy texture from oak aging that is lifted by a bright acidity, resulting in a complex and satisfying white wine.

From the windswept Santa Lucia Highlands, this Chardonnay is a brilliant expression of its cool-climate terroir. It entices with aromas of lemon curd, pineapple, and a touch of vanilla bean. The palate is a delightful balance of creamy texture and vibrant acidity, with flavors of ripe pear and toasted oak leading to a long, memorable finish.

Sourced from vineyards across Oregon, Firesteed Pinot Noir is a consistent and approachable example of the state’s signature grape. It presents a lovely bouquet of fresh red cherry, raspberry, and a subtle hint of earthy spice. The palate is smooth and light-bodied, with bright acidity and soft tannins that make it incredibly food-friendly.

This Pinot Noir is a testament to Hahn's estate vineyards in Monterey County. It offers a rich and inviting aromatic profile of black cherry, ripe strawberry, and a touch of cola. The palate is well-structured and smooth, with deep fruit flavors complemented by notes of vanilla and spice from oak aging, creating a sophisticated and balanced wine.

products.fullName: William Hill Cc Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: Sourced from California's vast and diverse Central Coast, this Pinot Noir is both elegant and expressive. It opens with delicate aromas of black cherry, raspberry, and a hint of dried herbs. The palate is medium-bodied with a silky texture, showcasing bright red fruit flavors and a touch of spice that is supported by soft, supple tannins.

Reflecting the rich terroir of Franciscan's estate vineyards, this Pinot Noir is crafted with a focus on balance and complexity. It features an alluring bouquet of ripe plum, black cherry, and subtle notes of mocha. The palate is velvety and smooth, with a core of concentrated dark fruit that is beautifully integrated with a hint of earthy spice.

A classic from one of Sonoma County's pioneering wineries, this Pinot Noir captures the essence of the Russian River Valley. It delivers an aromatic punch of red cherry, wild strawberry, and a touch of vanilla. The palate is silky and smooth, with a beautiful balance of fruit, acidity, and refined tannins that lead to a graceful, lasting finish.

Crafted by the talented team at Duckhorn, this Sonoma County Pinot Noir offers exceptional quality. It entices with a lovely bouquet of black cherry, strawberry, and a hint of rhubarb, complemented by notes of subtle oak spice. The palate is soft and silky, with a balanced acidity that makes it both appealing and incredibly versatile with food.

products.fullName: Talbott Kali Hart Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: Named for the founder's daughter, this Pinot Noir is a signature of Monterey's cool climate. From the family's Sleepy Hollow Vineyard, it displays vibrant aromas of cranberry, cherry, and vanilla. The palate is lush and inviting, with a rich texture and flavors of red fruit and spice that are carried by a bright acidity to a long, elegant finish.

The Santa Lucia Highlands imparts a distinct character to this expressive Pinot Noir. Its deep garnet color leads to aromas of black cherry, raspberry, and a touch of earthy forest floor. On the palate, the wine is rich and full-bodied for a Pinot, with concentrated fruit flavors, well-integrated tannins, and a whisper of spice on the finish.

A benchmark for Oregon's Willamette Valley, this Pinot Noir from Argyle is crafted with precision and elegance. It showcases a complex aromatic profile of dark cherry, pomegranate, and a hint of rose petal. The palate is refined and well-structured, with a silky texture, vibrant acidity, and a seamless integration of fruit, earth, and spice notes.

This California Sauvignon Blanc is a crisp, refreshing, and aromatic white wine. It greets the nose with vibrant scents of grapefruit, lime zest, and a hint of fresh-cut grass. The palate is zesty and clean, with a bright acidity that carries flavors of melon and passion fruit through to a lively, mouthwatering finish that is utterly delightful.

A celebrated classic from Sonoma County, this Fumé Blanc is a sophisticated and layered white wine. It is fermented in a mix of stainless steel and older oak barrels to build complexity, resulting in aromas of white peach, citrus, and a hint of vanilla. The palate is rich yet vibrant, with a creamy texture balanced by a crisp, refreshing acidity.

A unique Sauvignon Blanc-based blend from California, this wine from 19 Crimes offers a distinctive and fruit-forward profile. It opens with lively aromas of tropical fruit, candied pineapple, and a touch of citrus. The palate is crisp and bright with a hint of sweetness that makes it incredibly approachable and easy to enjoy on a warm day.

products.fullName: William Hill North Coast Sauvignon Blanc 750 Ml
products.description: Sourced from the premier vineyards of California's North Coast, this Sauvignon Blanc is a beautifully aromatic and refreshing wine. It presents a vibrant bouquet of Meyer lemon, ripe grapefruit, and a touch of fresh green herbs. The palate is crisp and clean, with a zesty acidity that highlights the bright citrus and tropical fruit flavors.

From the creative minds at Michael David Winery, this Lodi Sauvignon Blanc is anything but conventional. It is a bright and expressive wine, bursting with aromas of passion fruit, guava, and a hint of fresh jalapeño. The palate is zesty and full of energy, with a crisp acidity and a vibrant character that makes it a perfect warm-weather sipper.

Exhibiting the fresh, lively style that is a hallmark of the Decoy brand, this Sonoma County Sauvignon Blanc is incredibly refreshing. It leaps from the glass with tantalizing aromas of grapefruit, passion fruit, and lime. The palate is crisp and clean, with a vibrant acidity that is beautifully balanced by notes of sweet melon and a clean finish.

products.fullName: Frei Brothers Reserve Fume/Sauvignon Blanc 750 Ml
products.description: This Sauvignon Blanc from Sonoma County's Russian River Valley showcases the region's ability to produce vibrant and complex white wines. It offers an elegant aromatic profile of honeydew melon, white peach, and a hint of lemongrass. The palate is crisp and focused, with a refreshing acidity and a distinct minerality on its sophisticated finish.

A stunning example from a historic Napa Valley estate, this Sauvignon Blanc is made in the elegant Bordeaux style. It features a sophisticated nose of grapefruit, lime, and a touch of beeswax. The wine is fermented in a mix of stainless steel and neutral oak, which lends it a wonderful texture and complexity without masking its vibrant fruit character.

Hailing from Napa Valley, this Sauvignon Blanc from Rombauer is a vibrant and intensely aromatic wine. It bursts with aromas of key lime, mango, and passion fruit. On the palate, it is lively and bright, with a zesty acidity that is balanced by a touch of tropical sweetness. This is a bold and flavorful expression of California Sauvignon Blanc.

This delightful Prosecco from Italy is fresh, crisp, and incredibly festive. It offers delicate aromas of golden apple, white peach, and acacia flowers. The palate is light and refreshing, with a fine stream of bubbles and a clean, fruity character that is balanced by a touch of sweetness, making it a perfect aperitif or celebratory sparkling wine.

An authentic expression of Prosecco from the Veneto region of Italy, this bubbly is all about fresh, easy-drinking pleasure. It has an inviting nose of crisp green apple, pear, and a hint of citrus. The palate is light and zesty, with lively bubbles and a clean, off-dry finish that makes it an exceptionally versatile and crowd-pleasing sparkling wine.

Breaking the rules once again, 19 Crimes offers a unique California sparkling wine with a touch of sweetness. Cali Gold is a fruit-forward and approachable bubbly with notes of ripe pear, apricot, and a hint of honey. The palate is soft and easy-drinking, with a gentle effervescence that makes it a fun and festive choice for casual gatherings.

A remarkable sparkling wine from an unexpected place: New Mexico. Made using the traditional French Champagne method, this Brut offers surprising complexity and value. It features crisp aromas of green apple and citrus, with a hint of yeasty brioche. The palate is crisp and dry, with a fine mousse and a refreshing, mineral-driven finish.

This Prosecco is crafted to be a fresh and vibrant sparkling wine for any occasion. It opens with a delicate bouquet of white flowers, pear, and a touch of green apple. The palate is light-bodied and crisp, with a gentle fizz and a clean, off-dry character that makes it both refreshing on its own and a perfect partner for light appetizers and seafood.

This Sonoma County Sparkling Brut is a vibrant and energetic wine made for celebrating. It is crafted in a bright, crisp style, with lively aromas of green apple, citrus zest, and a hint of toasted brioche. The palate is zesty and refreshing, with a fine, persistent stream of bubbles and a clean, dry finish that leaves you wanting another sip.

This sparkling wine from J Vineyards is a beautifully blended cuvée of top California grapes. It is crafted in a crisp and refreshing style, with bright aromas of pear, grapefruit, and a touch of almond. The palate is lively and balanced, with a creamy texture from its fine bubbles and a clean, zesty finish that makes it incredibly versatile.

A beautiful and consistently delightful sparkling Rosé from one of California's most established producers. It shows off a pretty pink hue and offers alluring aromas of fresh strawberry, watermelon, and red cherry. The palate is crisp and refreshing, with a creamy texture and a bright fruitiness that makes it a festive and appealing choice.

Chandon's signature California Brut is a classic sparkling wine that consistently delivers quality and refreshment. It is a crisp and lively bubbly with notes of apple, pear, and citrus, accented by a hint of spice and almond. Its balanced profile and fine, persistent bubbles make it a versatile and reliable choice for any toast or celebration.
